{"tid":2043423,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺限聚令好似蘇b(蘇蛇）","createTime":"2020-05-30T11:52:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-18T06:46:31.000Z","uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"fb98a6254a5050816ac7eb1447146df67b1a2ee1","tid":2043423,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-30T11:52:24.000Z","msg":"Feel到就嚟收皮嗰陣就會有神秘力量吊住條命<br />\n<br />\n【更新報道】<br />\n<br />\n本港自 5 月 15 日起沒有本地感染個案，相隔 15 日後疑再次「斷纜」。<br />\n<br />\n至少兩個消息人士向《立場新聞》透露，威爾斯親王醫院一名病人初步確診，結果為強烈的陽性反應（Strong Positive），病人沒有外遊紀錄，現時正在深切治療部留醫，病人須使用呼吸機及強心藥。<br />\n<br />\n值得留意的是，病人現時仍屬初步確診，需待衞生署進行覆檢，才能證實是否確診。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fa386dbf1d6e9f4cbb497e94fb654fc03c140bd","tid":2043423,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d52fda0f88b2988e40b6900e05d0f4b9ea108dba","tid":2043423,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa386dbf1d6e9f4cbb497e94fb654fc03c140bd","tid":2043423,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:27:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d4a6fc59bbcdbd5a1b2b941ea7b687cf0af1261","tid":2043423,"uid":35348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d52fda0f88b2988e40b6900e05d0f4b9ea108dba","tid":2043423,"uid":44285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4fa386dbf1d6e9f4cbb497e94fb654fc03c140bd","tid":2043423,"uid":77092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-03T05:57:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-18T06:27:36.000Z